train() - Method in class nl.woetroe.nn.NeuralNetwork
Runs a single training-cycle, which consists of three processes feed-forward - the network computes the input to an output backpropagation - the network calculates the errors and signifies * how the weights should change to get a more accurate output updating the weights - the weights are actually adjusted
